title: [Parts of southwest Hamilton, including Ancaster, the Hamilton Beach Strip and part of Burlington, 1967] : [Flightline 674-403-Photo 100]
description: Shows parts of southwest Hamilton, west of James and south of Main. Includes Ancaster area. Includes construction of the Ancaster section of the Highway 403. Also four photographs showing the Beach Strip. Includes a small part of Burlington, but does not extend as far as Windemere Basin and Hamilton shore. Some are photocopies of originals from the Queen's University, Maps and Air Photos Collection. Source: [Ontario Department of Lands and Forests, Division of Surveys and Engineering, Aerial Surveys Section], November 1967.
publisher: [Ontario Department of Lands and Forests, Division of Surveys and Engineering, Aerial Surveys Section]
